race.description: Engineering By Stp Consultants Maiden Heat
race.comment: BOWL CUT JEAN (3) improved her time on first attempt here at the trip with a 0.8 lengths second in 19.77 latest. Smart run latest and looks a key chance here. GOLDSTAR EASTON (8) latest effort finished 4th in a Maiden on October 3 over 390m at this track behind Hara's Jackson beaten 9 lengths (22.55). Rates a key chance on best figures. PROFESSOR SAXON (1) has the advantage of a nice draw for his first outing. Worth keeping a close eye on the market. INLAND MARK (7) placed last time at this track and distance - worth some thought.
